        <title data-rh="true">cohost! - &quot;Back in early 2021, after reading some Engels,&quot;</title>
        <meta data-rh="true" name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="cohost"/><meta data-rh="true" name="application-name" content="cohost"/><meta data-rh="true" name="theme-color" content="#671A3D" media="(max-width: 1023px)"/><meta data-rh="true" name="theme-color" content="#83254f"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:site_name" content="Eric on cohost"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:title" content="Back in early 2021, after reading some Engels,"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:description" content="I wrote this blogpost [https://mokkograd.net/posts/2021-02-18-Individualsit%20production%20under%20capitalism] about how his descriptions of the early shift from individualised production of goods (=one person works to create something) to socialised production (=a lot of people work together to create something) under Capitalism reminded me how it feels to make games on your own, while having to sell them right next to AAA titles:

I&#x27;m not sharing this to do a &quot;go and read some theory, friends&quot;, but more because I&#x27;m really tired of seeing people try to fight this stuff on their own, when the only real way through this, is when we pool our resources and knowledge together.

I want for all of us to be in a better position to make the things that we want to make, and most of the things that would be needed for that are not possible without major political shifts across the entire world. However, I do believe that we all can do more to help each other, to pool our resources, to share knowledge. I&#x27;m very much to blame here as well, not because I don&#x27;t trust people, but because talking to them makes me scared and I also have this fundamental belief that I don&#x27;t have anything of value to offer to anyone. But I would like to help, as I would like for all of us to help each other.

(Apologies if this reads incoherent, it&#x27;s almost 1am over here and I was supposed to go to bed when I saw these posts)"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:type" content="article"/><meta data-rh="true" property="article:published_time" content="2024-01-23T23:48:06.193Z"/><meta data-rh="true" property="article:author" content="https://cohost.org/MOKKA"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:url" content="https://cohost.org/MOKKA/post/4263466-back-in-early-2021"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:image" content="https://staging.cohostcdn.org/avatar/7783-5df1d46c-b45a-414f-86a6-7932187d15b4-profile.png"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:image:alt" content="MOKKA"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:image:width" content="128"/><meta data-rh="true" property="og:image:height" content="128"/><meta data-rh="true" property="twitter:card" content="summary"/>
        

